The Lord of the rings was directed there, so there is a Hobbit village the most unusual landmark in that area.
New Zeland has also fresh air, it's a big deal for someone who live in Poland like me, so I was just walking and i started a nordic walking in beautiful mountains.
The views were breathtaking, I made thousands of photos during my holiday.
I was doing lot of sports, so i lost some pounds, so there is another advantage of active holiday.
What about disadvantages?
I cannot say that anything went wrong, everything was just as i planned and it was really motivating.
To be honest there is one thing i didn't like.
A very long travel by a plane.
It took 10 hours.
For me it's too much, but if someone doesn't care, holidays like this are without any disadvantages.
Dignity is the best quality for humans, if someone wants to become a really good person, it will be essential to be honest in all aspects of the life, such as being hard worker, good friend between friends, helping people each time that it can be possible do it, not injuring someone, at least conciously, or paying attention to need from others.
Our honestity will result seriously affected if we tell lies; Many people believe that it is important to always tell the truth, but in my opinion. there are some occasions when it is better do not tell exactly the truth, all the truth, because we can be talking about a painful topic about, or not be not the appropriate person to communicate all that we know, of course, It does not mean that we must to tell a lie, other possible situation is to have to tell a harmless lie, a white lie, to be polite and kind with a person, or in an particular situation; this is not to tell lies for me, it could be not to thell exactly the truth, but it would not be a serious sin.
Personally, in my life, I will always be against the lies, because they are the most pernicious things for our relatonships, and telling hard lies we would be considerer as a betrayer for anyone.
