When I was child, in primery school I had same teacher for five years.
I was lucky because the teaches was wonderfull.
She seemed love his job, and she had transmitted to this love to the students.
I have done this example to respond to the question if is good for students to have the same teacher for several years.
So, it depends on the teacher.
In my case during my childhood has been positive, but due too not all teacher are good in his job, maybe is better having new teachers eache year to avoid a negative situation with some bad teacher.
In that case you have to resist not more than one year.
Otherwise, method to teach are different depending on the teacher.
So, you have need a time to get used to a diferent method when you have a new teacher.
Furthermore you can have diferent point of view by different teacher about the same subject.
Then, the dibate is opened.
Some people state that you should change teachers to improve your skills, however I disagree, and I would like to study with same teacher.
That reason is as follows: First, it is imoportant to maintain relationship for everything.
When teacher teaches, he makes a menu.
For the sake of it, he thinks how and what he should do.
If I change teachers, the time lost.
That is not economy.
Second, one teacher has one advice, but teachers have several advice, so it creates confusion.
For education, it requires comprehension, so to study is essential from one teacher.
Orginally, in the minor field, there are not many teachers, and you cannot select the teachers.
Moreover, changing teachers do not produce good results.
To impreve is to make an effort by youself.
In my conclusion, a teacher is a teacher, it is issue weather you yourself challenge or not.
It is important how you find a best teacher.
