Video games are one of the most important industry since the end of the 20th century.
From the mere leisure at home controled by parents, it evolved to a real way of life difficult to keep under control with the developping of the Internet and the numbers of screens or other devices in our age .
Moreover, the marketing strategies of the video game companies aim to attract and keep people's attention.
Currently, we assist to a atention war between all theses companies.
In spite of the evolution, some parents can see a benefit by using it as way of education.
Taking a look at the video game history, we can measure its positive and negative impacts.
At the begining, the video allowed children to have fun during their free time.
In fact, each child had his game device in his house and could play alone or with friends.
In this period, mobile phones, internet and network didn't exist.
Children had to go in a specialized shop with their parents to buy each video games.
Downloading didn't exist.
Also, the few number of screesn present at home allows parents to keep this activity under control.
They were able to answer to the following questions: \u30FBWho my child is playing with? \u30FB
How long is playing? \u30FB
What sort of game is playing?
So, at the begining, video game appeared as a good way to make new friends.
The developping of Internet changed the rules at the end of th 90's.
Indeed, children have now the possibilty to when, where and how they want.
Parents have now a lot of difficulties to keep an eye on their children practiced due to the increasing of devices.
From a way to make real new friends, nework allows us to play with virtual unkonwon friends coming from all the world.
Currently, it is almost impossible for the parents to answer to the 3 questions see above.
However, some parents take advantage of this situation.
Internet offers new ways to improve skills and ability.
Children can learn speaking language or playing an instrument thank to internet and educative video games.
To conclude, it appears that video game can be benefit for children if their parent control the practice and offer other activities to keep good health.
