Experience with Write and Improve Introduction This report is about my personal experience with the Cambridge University's Write and Improve pregram available online which helps people in improving their writing skills.
Course Design Cambridge Write and Improve portal has very user friendly design which helps the user to choose their level of writing which is divided into four parts Beginner, intermediate, Advanced and Professional.
In every category they have topics with the difficulty level matching the level user haas opted to practise.
I chose intermediate level .
Once you are done with writing about the given topic you have to submit your content and after sometime you get feedback from the portal about your writing quality and with the feedback you can get a fair idea about your approach towards the topic and quality of sentence formation.
Variety of workbooks.
In write and Improve we get variety of different topics.
Some are logical ad some are essay driven.
Some topics require upated general knowlede.
It has something for everyone who really wants to improve their written english.
Conclusion I would strongly recommend this exercise to all the students of my class and to others .
You can try it irrespective of your age.
