My last vacation I went to Huatulco.
Huatulco is a handsome big town in Oaxaca, in the southeast of mexico .
The weather is very hot, ideal to enjoy a great landscape, maybe the best is a awesome long blue sea, ready to be surfed.
In the sea was seeing a great variety of marine animals, fish, whales and turtles.
The food is delicius, typical spicy Mexican food, the tlayudas, mole and different seafood dishes are the basis of "Oaxaque\u00F1a" gastronomy.
Then I tried the traditional drink in the region, mezcal, this alcoholic drink its strong and sour tasting, nothing special for me.
I was impacted with the Huatulco woman, gorgeous a short young girls are in the town and beach.
Near to the beach is a cheap small hotel, with some rooms and sea view, in which I stayed for three days.
The last vacacion I have a real good time with my family and friends.
Learning to speak foreign languages is definitely more important these days than it was before for a simple reason.
These days we have much more oportunities to use them.
Internet opened so many doors.
We have acces to sources that interest us in many languages, so it's useful to know them.
Because of the internet we can communicate with people from around the world - and that's why we learn their languages.
In past years learning other languages might be just a hobby.
Not everyone who learned foreign language had the possibility to go abroad to use it there.
Now we can use foreign languages without leaving our homes.
We can make friends with people from distant countries.
These days people also travel more, so knowing the language of the country you plan to go is useful, at least a few commonnest words.
My favourite season of the year is without the least doubt, summer.
The main reason for that is that I simply like when it's warm, and summer is the warmest season in Poland.
The average temperature is over 20 degrees which is perfect for me.
The days are long, it's only getting dark at about 10 pm.
I like it when it's bright, it boosts my energy.
What I also love about summer is the summer nature.
In this time of the year nature is in bloom.
The plants are green and the flowers are so colorful.
Another thing is that in summer I don't have to put on too many clothes, just a pair of jeans and a t-shirt and I'm ready to leave.
And also long days and warm weather encourage me to take more walks and even a summer rain isn't the obstacle.
