The school have transformed in the last ten years.
The conectivity and social media created a new world that the academic institutions can not ignore, because the new generations have a different idea about knoledge and learning process.
This new reality impacts in differents topics of the school, an example is the teenageres don't have interes in philosofy or histtory.
The institutions have to think furhter than the obsolete estructures of learning.
One of the goals that they have to work on is the strategy of improve the methods of teaching.
Platforms like Vimeo or Youtube deliver the same role that the master class, so it is a mistake thinking that the students only go to the institutions for master class.
In that order, the School of the future needs to incorporate the idea of realease the knowledge, and offers a new topic to integrate the theory and laboral practicse.
In summary, the students of the future won't study for knowledge, because they already have it.
They will search a platform to improve their methods of studying and how they can incorporate to their labor life.
Hendaye is a very exciting place to be.
Our city is visited by tourists from all over the world.
Coming Hendaye is an opportunity to see and do a lot of things.
First, if you come visit us, you have to see two main touristic places: the beach and the climb.
You will enjoy one of the most clean and large beach in the South West of France.
Also, from the summit of the climb, yoo will apreciate a beatiful over the beach.
Then, if you are an outgoing person and you are interested in culture, you will discover our various parks and museum.
Indeed, in Hendaye, there is many parks allowing us to relax in a friendly environment.
Moreover, from Hendaye, you can reach several museum located around the city.
For example, you will find out the origin and the history of the basque culture in the Bayonne museum.
To conclude, food is also part of our culture.
In Hendaye, you will taste many local food specialities.
We are looking forward to hearing from you
