There are four seasons in the world.
They are spring, summer, autumn and winter.
But in our country, Myanmar, 5here are only three seasons.
They are the hot season, the rainy season and the cold season.
Each season has enjoyable weathers and each season is for four months long.
Among them, my favorite season of the year is the cold season.
It is from November to February.
In the cold season, the weather is very cool and pleasant.
Because of the cold weather, we can live comfortably in the day time and sleep soundly at night.
It is also a good time to travel from one place to another because there is no dust or no mud in this season.
It is a good season both for old people and for students.
The old people walk in the morning to be healthy and we, the students usually get up early and study our lessons to pass the examination easily.
It is also a good time to study because our body is active, our mind is clear and our brain is fresh.
These are the reasons why the cold season is my favorite season of the year.
