For everyone who studys English, I recommend Write and Improve (W&I) because it is very usuful tools.
I can point out those advantage much. I would like to mention specific reasons as follows.
At first, I would explain W&I.
This is checked system regarding English Sentences using IT technology.
It shows various themes, learners composite about the themes.
As soon as learners submit their composition, the system evaluate grammar and vocabrary.
As the results, leraners know true expression.
This service is free of charge amazingly.
For learning English, you usually go to school and study yourself reading a textbook.
The English conversation program that you talk about teachers is expensive sinse calicuram costs.
In case of self-study, it is difficult to keep motivating.
