In my best holiday ever I went to Peru.
I remember that I earned a lot of money to plain the adventure to travel across de Country in four months.
Perhaps I feel that holiday was so special to me because I worked to hard to enjoyed it.
In the Country, I visited fourteen cities.
I knew all the principal and most beautifull places that the Incas culture left to the history.
I went to Machi Pichu, there was so special because I had to camping on the trains road.
At the night, I have to covered myself because It was so cold.
But it didn't matters to me: I was so excited to know the most important arquitectonic monumient in south America.
What I felt when I sow the monument changed me.
The meeting between global history and my personal life just gave to me a new perspective about everything.
In that holiday I discovered that the hard working, discipline and enthisasm are the tools to catch up your dreams.
The new wave of travel At the actual times travel is a neccesity for bussiness, economy and entretainment.
People wants to know every little thing on earth.
The international economy found a new tool to explore in travel, the future will need a new posibilities to offer more advance, ecologic and confortable methods to travel.
From my perspective the central point of the debt is on environmental problems with the develop of travelers.
The thecnologies we have are not prepare to the environemntal goals that the humanity stablished in the first decade of the century.
For that reason, travel need to think another strategies to offer travel according this kind of neccesities.
Another important topic is the bank regulations across the world.
One of the problems with travel is that the countrys on way to develop doesn't have the same posibillities to find a place in the new world.
Money exchange is the principal problem, so I think create new coperations groups between countrys will provide persons the alternative to travel without waste to much money in travel.
Countries need to reduce the cost in transport and direct the money of the traveler in the national market.
