We the people shape the upcoming future for the improvement in living standards, for the betterment of future and for the mankind.
Therefore health of the kids / teenagers is absolutely essential and important as their education.
Our world is changing.
We are facing unprecedented challenges that the world has never faced before and therefore it is crucial for the young generation to stay fit and healthy as a healthy man is always a asset to the country's overall development.
But things are becoming worse nowadays.
Schools are providing with so much homework that the kids are not getting enough time to go outside and play.
Kids nowadays have less patience, and they are not able to work in team, they are becoming more and more dependant on their parents for almost everything.
This is a big issue and it needs to be addressed.
Adding to this is their eating habits.
They always want something that suits their tongues.
Due to this they can't tolerate and can mange different conditions that is very important.
Because of the negative effects on health of an inactive lifestyle, all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week.
Let them glide in the highest skies or swim in the deepest ocean.
Let them open their mind and allow them to have time with their friends.
This will not only allow them to with their friends and work in team but it will bring the qualities in them that is very important for the upcoming generation.
We aren't defined by our past but yes we are defined by our present.
We need kids to have patience and they will definitely start having a health eating habits.
Therefore it is important to force university students / school students to do sport activities at least 3 times per weak.
