The best holiday that I remember has been in my childhood.
It is a little bit pity that I cannot remember when exactely it was maybe because I have some confused memories about those very far years.
So, It is better if I talk about some recent holidays like when I spent a period doing a travel well knowed as"Camino de Santiago."
I travelled on bicycle sharing that experience with a friend.
So, we began the travel from Mallorca to Barcelona on the boat where we spent an enjoyable time.
In early afternoon we toke the bus to Pamplona where the route began.
The idea was to do all the pilmigrage route, so we turn back to the frontier close to France cycling.
Once reached "Ronchesvalles" we came back to Pamplona where there was "San Fermin" festival knowed in all the worl.
There we spent too much time because the ambient was funny.
We had some problemto find a place somewhere to sleep, but lukely we found a templarian hostel where in spit of there were no bed, the owner give us the option to sleep in the church.
Every day was an adventure, for this reason I remind that holiday as one of the best ones.
