Nowadays , there are more and more people dedicated their time to learning English .
Although most of us try to improve our listening and speaking skills , many people are trying to improve their writing skill .
So what do they do to get the goal that they set ?
Well , there are many ways such as going to a club , do a course but let me tell you a tool that is very helpful in making your writing skills be better .
That is Write&Improve .
First , it's free .
You just need to have a mobile phone or a computer or an Ipad which can connect to Internet well .
You can do any tasks you want at any time you want .
And it's so great that you don't have to spend any money on it .
Why do we need an expensive course when we can improve our writing skill with a free tool.
Secondly , there are hundreds of tasks for you and you even can creat a progress for only you .
These tasks are ordered in many levels such as beginner , intermediate or advanced .
There are also workbooks created for business field or just for fun which helps us be more creative with the funny stories , poems or passages.
And if you need to improve your English writing skill for IELTs exams or the similar exams , don't worry there are test zones for IELTS academic or IELTs General Training or B2 .
W&I never stops updating and selecting more interesting tasks .
I guess that you have a question:" It is free and sounds good but is it really helpful ?
How do we know where the mistakes are?
If we don't pay , will the experts check our articles ? " .
And my answer is "Yes" , after we send our article , in a blink of an eye , the feedback will appear and show our mistakes and we can see our changes , too .
We can know how long we finish a task in "Task time" and there are clues describing the content of the task (often by words but sometimes by images).
Not only that , once a week , they send us some tips to improve our writing .
We also know our progress or which level our task in .
We also have awards to encourage our trying .
However , I have some difficulties that sometimes , W&I don't check the mistakes right .
But I must say that this is the best tool to improve our writing skill.
From Duelwen.
