For my money, I would like to live a long and calm life until 100 years old rather than living an intense short life.
A calm life is what everybody seeks and strives to have.
Peace of mind and a healthy body are what a calm life offers.
Why would I choose an intense and unsafe life while I can have a much better one for a long happy time!
With a calm and long life, I can suck the spirit of life, enjoy the very moment and collect the best of reminiscences.
I shall see my grandchildren hopping about around me and witness the progress of humanity.
My philosophy of life is to take things easy and consider any step I want to take so that I would not regret later.
Besides, I believe that having a short but intense life has fallen from favour by the majority of humans.
Thanks to the incredible progress of medicine and the breakthroughs of technology, we, humans, can experience high quality living unlike our ancestors whose life was threatened by diseases, unmerciful plagues and prolong disastrous wars.
With all the benefits modern life offers, I do not fathom why I would choose a short life.
Previous research remained in the shadow of uncertainty whereas new studies have elucidated a lot of mysteries about life.
In fine, I would never ever choose a short life.
