Review on write and improve Write and improve is the new tool I have discovered for learning English - a live feedback giving platform.
Firstly, I find really adequate the organisational structure of the tasks - 3 notebooks for each of the 3 levels: beginner, intermediate and advance according to the CEFR levels and also one notebook for the business jargon.
I know from experience that you should start from lower levels in order to make progress, albeit you're an experienced speaker, because if you target a more demanding task you'll not be focused enough to finish your composition and you are going to finish up disappointed and bored and closing the internet.
Secondly, I enjoyed the means of costumization as the recording of feedbacks, the graph of improvements and also making your own notebooks and even your own tasks like a teacher does.
All this comforted me and made me feel like I was having my own tutor aside me.
Last but not least, I haven't encountered any technical problem as the waiting spans were off the shortest.
Even if the software had been slower I couldn't have complained because all other features are great and the speed of the site can only be seen as a major advantage.
All in all, I recommend write and improve by my heart to all newbies but also advanced learners and I also recommend them to make a schedule and to increase to frequency and the difficulty level of the compositions gradually.
