First of al, Write and Improve is the suitable website for me to ameliorate the writing skill.
There is no doubt about the numerous advantages.
Since I started using W&I, the level rised clearly.
From level A1 to B1, maybe for somepeople this is not such a huge change.
However, from someone who can not even type words correctly into that level B1, that is clearly showing the difference.
When using W&I, you can recieved guidance to improve your essay.
It also demonstrate your progress, so that you can know what to try out next.
The other side of the coin is W&I still having a little error.
The mark is comparative and not always perfect.
Some words and structure is grammatically correct but W&I would say the opposite.
That is the thing i do not like about it.
Besides, everything else is quite good and convenient for beginner.
To sum up, I think Write and Improve is may not the best one for you to learn, but it the suitable one for you to take first steps.
Moreover, I would recommend it to my friends, colleguages and everybody I know
