Music is the essence of expressions, feelings, emotions being stringed together using harmony of sound to create a masterpiece.
Music is a form of art of expressing your inner feelings using sound.
Sometimes, things do not need to be listened to, they need to be felt.
In such cases, words fail and music succeeds.
Many times in our lives, when we are feeling a particular emotion, having those hormones flowing through us, we seek a particular way to show it.
A smile infused with music and dance can clearly depict that you are happy.
That is the purpose of music.
To depict, amplify your inner emotions to an external world.
In movies, we have experienced how fantastically music can change the atmosphere of the room.
Whether it is a Jonathan Larson musical or a battle scene, no scene will be felt if it wasn't for the background music, which makes us feel as if we are also experiencing that scene.
That's how the music industry works.
They amplify the range of the particular scene or feeling to a broad audience, making everyone a part of this one large group.
Music is an essential part of human excistence.
As an art expression, people needs to express the conection between their souls and the rytmin in nature.
Due to channel of comunication, music is the best way to show emotions.
Thus, this kind of art became in a reflection of the scence of human being.
Since the dawn of societies, people has been expressed theirself by music.
the conections and the simply prathrons of ritmyn creates the perfect admosphere to collect the feelings and social ideas in a determinate place and time.
The human connection with music were produced as soon as men learnt how to manipulate the production of sound.
In the evolution of west and east civiliztions, Music occupied a privilige position like the symbol of different times.
For instance, in XX century, specially the time between wars, the national hymns and popular music fought for the recognotion and the representative part in National's history.
All things considered, our life and history couldn't exist if we would never found our human connection with sound. All things
We need music in our lives, but each person with your style and time.
Music can make us feel good or not, it will depend why the sound will come to us.
A person listening to music that don't like it, this is harmful.
In this way, music will not always be beneficial.
For exemple, I could live without music than listen to bad music.
I prefer hear the sound of the nature or the traffic than a bad music.
