Hello Sam, long time no see!
How have you been!
I really hope this message finds you marvelous.
Frankly, I am so excited for your visited.
After two long years that we are only online study budy finally I could meet you!
At the first instance I want to say thank you for your support, some months ago I were incapable to write an English sentence and now I can write down a full letter.
On the other hand, it is great that finally you decidered visit my country, Mexico.
It will be a great opportunity to improve my English skills, especially my speaking, and you could taste the great variety of Mexican dishes, you will enjoy them!
For the last three days, I have been cleaning my house and decorated your room, you have to stay at my house all your vacation so you don\u00B4t have to care about hotel or book an house.
I want to ask to you What time and day will you arrive to the airport?
I could pick up as soon as posible, my dad could lend me his car so don\u00B4t worry about that!
Oh I least forget!
Don\u00B4t be cringe!
You will love my family and the Mexican people, they are kind and respectful with the foreign.
The next day, I could give you a tour in Mexico City, we will go to the Arena Mexico to watch the Mexican wrestlers, it is one of the most important and weird tradition in my town, then, we will visit some of the most emblematic museums around here.
It is not for show off, but Mexico City has the most of museums of Latin America.
It should be a surprise, but I don\u00B4t with this for more time, this week my favorite soccer team plays the final match and I have two tickets for the event, they sold out in only ten minutes but fortunately I got two!
You don\u00B4t have to brind anything, everything is ready for your vacation, only you have to enjoy your time to spare, it will be worthwhile!
What do you think?
Please send me a message in the nexts days with your comments Take care, your friend Yisus.
