Most of the countries have four seasons but there are only three seasons in my country, Myanmar.
We don't have spring and autumn like others.
All we have are summer, rainy season and the cold season but the climate of the regions are really different.
In summer, Yaynankyant and Yangon are hotter than other cities in the countries.
So I live in Yangon and I hate summer because I feel as if I am in the hell in summer.
I love cool and cold weather but I don't like wet.
Therefore my choice is the cold season.
In the cold season, there is no snow in my city and to say the truth I have never seen snow.
I like doing sports like riding bicycle and running, as you know the cold season is the best season to do sports.
Drinking coffee with mist is the most pleasant time in my life.
We usually cook steamed sticky rice with dry fish, add some sesame oil and stir them.
That is really delicious.
If I have numerous money, I will build the city where always cold and I live there for good.
