I really want to go to your party and have a great time together, but I have to say I am sorry.
It is a pity, but I will not assit.
Let me explain it.
Next Saturday I will be workload.
In the morning, I will have my English class, my final exam is comming so I can not skip it.
In fact, I am nervous because I will have a speaking test, I am improving a lot but my speaking it is not my fortress so wish me luck.
After that I am going to go to my school graduation.
Needless to say that I am a science teacher in the small high school in Mexico City.
Next Saturday, it will be my first students graduation.
I am proud with my students performance and I am feeling blue in the same time, because they will go to the university and I won\u00B4t see them anymore.
Finally, I won\u00B4t have a free night.
Next, I am going to go to my grandmother\u00B4s house.
It will be her birthday and my relativies throw a family gathering.
In spite of, I can not go to your celebration, I have bought a present for you.
Next Monday I will have some time to spare, maybe we can hang around, maybe we could have a beer or only an icream, don\u00B4t worry about money, it\u00B4s on me.
What do you think?
