In my opinion, learning to speak a foreign language is still important.
On the one hand, learning a foreigh language is necessary for works or better prospects.
And learning a new language may help you solve more problems while traveling.
On the other hand, I think the language and culture go hand in hand.
For example, imagine trying to learn about American culture without understanding English, that you can\u2019t understand the country\u2019s humor and jokes, as well as books.
So, I think the cultural subtleties and pop culture references might be totally lost without some grasp of the local language.
And, no matter in the past or present, learing a new language make you smater and can lead your live to a new level.
Overall, these are the reason that why I think learning to speak a foreign language is still important now.
