Hello Alex I am really sorry to tell you that I will not be able to join you on for your Saturday afternoon party.
My family is visiting me this week-end and I haven't seen them all for a long time.
I hope you will understand.
May I suggest that we meet up in the next coming week-ends and we hence be free to catch up anytime.
I would propose that we organise to have lunch with some other friends that we haven't met for years and it would be great to spend some time together for lunch and plan some activities in the afternoon.
I will be available anytime to talk in the next 48 hours.
I hope you will have a nice weather and a lovely time for your party.
Sorry for changing of plans.
I will contact you the following day to have so news of your party.
Take care
Dear Sam: I want to talk to you about tomorrow.
You can come over when you prefer, but I won't be at home until 6 p.m. due to my work.
My boss is a totally idiot: he told to me today I have to work tomorrow despite the fact that I asked him for a free day.
Besides, my boss gave his girlfriend the day off.
That's why I have to work tomorrow, because he want to favor his girlfriend.
However, you can come over whenever you want because here will be my wife and a few friends.
By the way, did you met Matt?
I'm going to the my wife to introduce you to him, because I think you have a lot in common.
You asked me if you must bring something the other day.
Only if you could, do you mind bring some of that delicious chicken salad that you made for your birthday?
I felt in love with your chicken salad.
You asked too about how to get to my house.
It's pretty easy: you must drive south on the town hall to the country until you see two red chalets.
My house is the red chalet at the left of the high road.
See you soon.
Dear Alex. How is it going?
I hope you are well.
I am very sad because I can't come to your party.
I am very sorry about that.
I know I should to be with you because this is important day but I have some excuse.
You will understand when you read this email.
I quit my job because our company is broken.
Guest what is next?
Yes, you are right.
I don't have enough money for living in London.
I can not pay my bills.
The life is expensive here.
I have to find a job.
So that is why I can not come to your country, to your party.
Even I come and turn back, I will have jobless and homeless.
I must do something for living.
I hope you forgive me.
Let's do things like this.
I will have find jop approximality one or two months after.
So I can come to you.
How is it?
Hello Chris, I want to ask you if you'll finally come with me and my family to the science museum next Saturday.
I know that you told me that you would come, but, after what happened, I'm not sure.
Your father has had a stroke a car accident a few days ago, and besides the fact that he's all right, I don't know if you'll be allowed to come with us.
I look forward to going to the museum with you, but if you don't feel comfortable, we should do it in other moment.
In case you come, we'll go to the museum in my father's car.
If you want, we can pick you up in your home and go together.
There will be a magnificent exposition about the human evolution this weekend, and a showing about how volcanos works organized by some chemists.
We could see it if you want, but we would spend all day on the museum, because the exposition is only open in the morning, and the showing is in the afternoon.
You don't have to bring anything.
My father has already bought the tickets, and he said me that we could pay him washing his car next weekend.
See you later.
Hi Alex, I'm writing to tell you a bad thing.
Unfortunately, I won't be able to come on your party this Saturday afternoon.
I'm really sorry but the reason I couldn't come is that I will take a fly for Dublin.
This week I'm going to visit the city of Dublin, I have been decided to stay for three days.
I will spend time with my girlfriend.
I have bought plane tickets two months ago, when there was a huge discount on the website of the company.
Could we meet on Friday night?
It is just a suggestion, in that case we must share a bike and go around the National park and have an enjoyable tour of it.
If Friday doesen't go well for you, I may suggest the 1st of october, when I am going to do my birthday party in my parents house near London, there will be lots of people.
wishing you lot of fun for your party, See you soon, Luca
Yes, we do.
Music has always been an important part of the human beings' lifes since always.
Actually many historicians and archaeologists have been able to demostrate that primitive persons, hundreds of thousands years ago, already used the music, and play some instruments like drums and flutes.
Music can help us in many ways.
Music can help us to calm and relax, to express sad emotions, or to have a fun time.
Besides, music can help us to manage hard times and moments on our lifes, like a break up or the dead of someone dear.
I myself usually listen to rock music when I'm angry, and calm and beautiful music when I'm sad or nostalgic.
Furthermore, we can use the music to show our emotions and feelings for someone.
Actually, many people use music to tell someone that they are in love with them.
For all this reason, a life without music wouldn't be the same.
Plus, for many people music are their job.
What would they do without music then?
Well, I usually need to sleep in a dark and quiet room, withtout lights and noise.
Besides, I need clean sheets and a warm blanket.
I've slept in this way since I was a child, and I don't have any intention to change it.
However, some times I've could manage to sleep in worse conditions, for example, when I've been very tired or drunk.
Anyway, I need dark and silence to sleep because I usually have a lot of problems to fall sleep.
I only sleep at night, and only for a few hours.
I always try to sleep the eight hours that the doctors recommended, but I rarely can do it.
Dear Jon: I'm glad you emailed me.
Well, there are a lot of wonderful foods in my country, Spain, and a I like many of them.
That's why it's pretty difficult to me choose only one of them.
Among my favorite foods are meatballs, croquettes or spaghetti carbonara.
However, my favorite among all is undoubtedly stewed lentils.
I've loved this dish since I was a child, and I've eaten it al least once a week since then.
I usually eat stewed lentils to meal, although I've eaten for dinner too sometimes.
I like stewed lentils because is a very tasty food, and very nutritive too.
Hello Alex First of all, thanks a lot for inviting me your party.
I would like to attend your party but my uncle is going to come to Turkey from French.
I have to meet them.
He called me two week ago.
He will stay about a week in here with him family.
I have not seen almost two years.
If I confess, I miss them and him children.
